{"data":[{"id":564004951,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fd51f37ac298387052e18e73158e3187","url_token":"reallysugar","name":"无色方糖","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/1eba86958dff6ee3d6ae09539e40c30b_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/1eba86958dff6ee3d6ae09539e40c30b_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fd51f37ac298387052e18e73158e3187","user_type":"people","headline":"再发芽的小透明","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":257732,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564004951","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546320252,"updated_time":1546326246,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":156,"comment_count":22,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e别的答主已经说了逻辑上的错误在哪，我来还原一下 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 的思路。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他引入“-1”作为负质数，本质是\u003cb\u003e使得2符合\u003c/b\u003e哥德巴赫猜想变式（\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"2\\in{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（同时囊括了这一命题：\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cforall%7Bn%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C\" alt=\"\\forall{n}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-1%29%2B%282n%2B1%29%2C2n%2B1%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BP%7D\" alt=\"2n=(-1)+(2n+1),2n+1\\in\\mathbb{P}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e。）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为了证明弱哥猜（即原文中的哥德巴赫猜想变式），他需要证明以下逆否命题为真。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e若\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists%7Bn_0%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n_0%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"\\exists{n_0}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n_0\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e，则\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e不是质数。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e注意，“-1是负质数”是人为提出的概念，因此这是一个结论恒假的命题。若要证明这一命题为真，必须证明其条件为假。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e到这里他的思路出现问题了。他本该证明\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists%7Bn_0%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n_0%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"\\exists{n_0}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n_0\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 为假。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（事实上如果该条件为真，即存在偶数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n_0%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"2n_0\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，那他就推翻了哥猜。）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但其实他做的工作其实是：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e若\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"2\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e，则\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e不是质数。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"2\\in{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e是他定义负质数后的必然结果，所以产生了一个条件恒假的真命题。这一工作不存在任何意义，也无法证明上述存在命题为真。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e他在这里混淆了证明存在命题的方式，把“若存在”和“存在若”搞混了。 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 自己的专栏也提到了这一点。\u003cbr\u003e另外，他被“条件恒假的命题恒真”这一情况彻底搞蒙了，被自己绕了进去。\u003cbr\u003e同时，他定义的A以及k，只是在自身的定义里循环论证，自始至终都只是在折腾自己，没有对哥猜产生影响。\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e实际上，为了证明上述逆否命题为真（即其条件为假），他要做的其实是证明：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cforall%7Bn%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n%5Cin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"\\forall{n}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n\\in{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但这就是他弱哥猜命题的结论，又回到最初的起点。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e引入负质数“-1”没有对证明猜想起到任何帮助。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我在初中的时候一度以为是自己手算出了海伦公式，但其实秦九韶比我早了快八百年了。人偶尔觉得自己是真理的中心是一件很正常的事，但要看清现实。（好在我的初中数学老师只靠一次罚站就让我看清了现实）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e希望能维持这份热情用到正确的方向，踏实学习，那愿你前程远大。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e完。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"别的答主已经说了逻辑上的错误在哪，我来还原一下 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 的思路。 他引入“-1”作为负质数，本质是\u003cb\u003e使得2符合\u003c/b\u003e哥德巴赫猜想变式（2\\in{A}）。（同时囊括了这一命题：\\forall{n}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n=(-1)+(2n+1),2n+1\\in\\mathbb{P}。）为了证明弱哥猜（即原文中…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2C